Spring Break was fun, i dug it.. i am not so excited to get back into the daily grind. Like i said i had fun but i find myself going, what did i do all week? i am now playing checkers with my client and getting paid for it. i love my job!

mmmm today was great, except for the dog sitting and being away from home and ian for so long... we had v-day saturday adn he did really well... i was very proud of him and his skillz.  anyway work has its good and bad moments... it is a good day if there are only about 3 bad.  Tomorrow should be tricky but i am up to the challange and should get along just fine... now to smoke and drink about going back to the dog...

So i am currently working and decided the old lj had to go and the new one was sooooo in.   Ian now lives with me and this rocks my tiny world.  I am dogsitting next week and that is not oh so cool.  I have another new car and this one should last more than six months.  School is taking it out of me but what can you do...
